%b
  Home Page Content
%br
(This is the text that gets displayed on the front page of the portal, before a user has logged in.
%br
Clear everything from this editor and save the settings to reset the content to default.)
- home_page_text_area_id = dom_id_for(admin_settings, :home_page_content, :textarea)
= f.text_area :home_page_content, :id => home_page_text_area_id, :class => 'mceNoEditor'
%input{:type=>"button", :value=>"Preview Home Page", :onclick=>"preview_home_page('#{home_page_text_area_id}', null);", :class=>"button", :style=>"margin-top: 10px; font-size: 13px"}
%br
%br
= f.label :wrap_home_page_content, "Wrap Home Page Content", :style => "display:inline;"
= f.check_box :wrap_home_page_content
%br
Select 'Wrap Home Page Content' to include the Portal banner,
project cards, and 'featured content' when displaying custom home page content.
This is the default.
